#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&granatier; is a clone of the classic &nbsp;"
"<trademark><application>Bomberman</application></trademark> game, inspired "
"by the work of the <application>Clanbomber</application> clone."
msgstr ""
"El &granatier; és un clon del joc <trademark><application>Bomberman</"
"application></trademark> clàssic, inspirat en el treball del clon "
"<application>Clanbomber</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The object of the game is to run through an arena, using bombs to clear out "
"blocks and eliminate your opponents. Several bonuses and handicaps are "
"hidden underneath the blocks &ndash; these can either help or hinder your "
"progress."
msgstr ""
"L'objectiu del joc és córrer per un camp de batalla, utilitzant bombes per a "
"aclarir blocs els i eliminar els adversaris. Sota els blocs s'oculten "
"diverses bonificacions i desavantatges -poden ajudar o dificultar el vostre "
"progrés-."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>A &granatier; screenshot</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Una captura de pantalla del &granatier;</screeninfo>"

